{"lemma":"غَلّاتُ","slug":"غَلّاتُ","root":"غ.ل.ل","root_slug":"غ-ل-ل","root_link":"/words/roots/غ-ل-ل","pos":"N","pos_camel":"noun","paradigm":[],"frequency_in_corpus":0,"cross_references":{"qac":{"found":false},"wiktextract":{"found":true,"entry_count":2,"pos_tags":["noun"],"has_etymology":true,"sense_count":2},"lanes":{"found":true,"entry_ids":["n32159","n32168","n32169"],"search_url":"https://lanelexicon.com/?s=%D8%BA%D9%8E%D9%84%D9%91%D8%A7%D8%AA%D9%8F"}},"translations":null,"definition":{"source":"wiktextract","senses":[{"pos":"noun","gloss":"yield, produce, return"},{"pos":"noun","gloss":"verbal noun of غُلَّ (ḡulla) (form I)","tags":["form-of","noun-from-verb"]}]},"etymology":{"source":"wiktextract","text":"Instance noun of غَلّ (ḡall), verbal noun of غَلَّ (ḡalla, “to yield”)."},"ipa":["/ɣal.la/","/ɣul.la/"],"lanes_definition":{"source":"lanes","entries":[{"entry_id":"n32159","headword_ar":"غَلَّهُ","root":"gl","body":[{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K, *) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~N","text_ar":"غَلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made it,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"caused it, to enter,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K, * [in the CK"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Audoxila","text_ar":"اُدْخِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is erroneously put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^adoxala","text_ar":"اَدْخَلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":",])"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fiY","text_ar":"فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$aYo'K","text_ar":"شَىْءٍ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"into a thing;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(O, K;) as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galogalahu","text_ar":"غَلْغَلَهُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, * TA,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galogalapN","text_ar":"غَلْغَلَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; or this last word signifies the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"making,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"causing,"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to enter"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"so as to become confused with, and a part of, that into which it enters:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) ―         -b2-  and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~a","text_ar":"غَلَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) aor. as above, (S) and so the inf. n., (TK,) signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"It entered"},{"kind":"text","text":"[into a thing]; (S, O, K;) being intrans. as well as trans.; (S, O;) and so does ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ainogal~a","text_ar":"اِنْغَلَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tgl~l","text_ar":"تغلّل","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tagalogala","text_ar":"تَغَلْغَلَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"; (K, TA;) said of [what are termed by logicians] substances and of [what are termed by them] accidents. (TA.) ―         -b3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yagul~u","text_ar":"يَغُلُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a ram means"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Penem suum inserit"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yudoxilu qaDiybahu","text_ar":"يُدْخِلُ قَضِيبَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":")"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"non sublatâ caudâ."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, * TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~a","text_ar":"غَلَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Inivit"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ha$aA^a","text_ar":"حَشَاَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in some copies of the K without the hemzeh,) feminam: (K, TA; in which latter is added"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wlA ykwn Al~A mn DaxomK","text_ar":"ولا يكون الّا من ضَخْمٍ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[app. meaning that this is not said of any but such as is big, or bulky]:) mentioned by IAar. (TA.) ―         -b4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~a Ald~uhona fiY","text_ar":"غَلَّ الدُّهْنَ فِى"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"raA^osihi","text_ar":"رَاْسِهِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made the oil to enter amid the roots of the hair of his head."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~a $aEarahu biAlT~iybi","text_ar":"غَلَّ شَعَرَهُ بِالطِّيبِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made the perfume to enter amid his hair."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b5-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~ahu lahu","text_ar":"غَلَّهُ لَهُ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He made it to be unapparent to him"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"das~ahu lahu","text_ar":"دَسَّهُ لَهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he"},{"kind":"text","text":"[the latter]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"having no knowledge of it."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA: in which the pronoun affixed to the verb relates to a dagger, and to a spear-head.) ―         -b6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~a AlmafaAwiza","text_ar":"غَلَّ المَفَاوِزَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He"},{"kind":"text","text":"(a man)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"entered into the midst of the deserts,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"waterless deserts."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) ―         -b7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~a AlmaA='u bayona AlA^a$ojaAri","text_ar":"غَلَّ المَا=ءُ بَيْنَ الاَشْجَارِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K,) aor."},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The water ran amid the trees."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"AlmaA='u fiY Al$~ajari","text_ar":"المَا=ءُ فِى الشَّجَرِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"tagalogala","text_ar":"تَغَلْغَلَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"The water entered amid the breaks,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"interspaces, of the trees."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S.) ―         -b8-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~a AlgilaAlapa","text_ar":"غَلَّ الغِلَالَةَ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He clad himself with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wore, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"glAlp","text_ar":"غلالة"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] (K, TA)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"beneath the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garments;"},{"kind":"text","text":"because he who does so enters into it. (TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Alv~awoba","text_ar":"الثَّوْبَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aigotalalotu","text_ar":"اِغْتَلَلْتُ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"[in like manner] signifies"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I clad myself with,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wore, the garment beneath the"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"other"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"garments."},{"kind":"text","text":"(K.) ―         -b9-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~a fulaAnFA","text_ar":"غَلَّ فُلَانًا"},{"kind":"text","text":", (K, TA,) aor. and inf. n. as above, (TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He put upon the neck,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the hand, of such a one, the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gul~","text_ar":"غُلّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"ring,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"collar, of iron,"},{"kind":"text","text":"for the neck, or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pinion"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"manacle"},{"kind":"text","text":"for the hand]. (K, TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gul~a","text_ar":"غُلَّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He had the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gul~","text_ar":"غُلّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put upon him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, * TA.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galalotu yadahu A_iliY Eunuqihi","text_ar":"غَلَلْتُ يَدَهُ اـِلِى عُنُقِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I confined his hand to his neck with the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gul~","text_ar":"غُلّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (S, O.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~a A^asiyrFA bigul~K","text_ar":"غَلَّ اَسِيرًا بِغُلٍّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mino qid~K waEalayohi $aEarN","text_ar":"مِنْ قِدٍّ وَعَلَيْهِ شَعَرٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He confined a captive with a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gul~","text_ar":"غُلّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of thongs upon which was hair"},{"kind":"text","text":"]. (TA.) One says,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"maA lahu A^ul~a wagul~a","text_ar":"مَا لَهُ اُلَّ وَغُلَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K, TA, [in some copies of the S and K, which have misled Golius and Freytag,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mAlh A^ul~N wagul~N","text_ar":"ماله اُلٌّ وَغُلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) a form of imprecation, (K, TA,) meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"What ails him?"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"may he be thrust,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pushed, in the back of his neck, and become possessed,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"insane,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(IB, TA in the present art. and in art."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Al","text_ar":"ال"},{"kind":"text","text":",)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and therefore have the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gul~","text_ar":"غُلّ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"put upon him."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA in the present art.) And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gul~ato yaduhu A_ilaY Eunuqihi","text_ar":"غُلَّتْ يَدُهُ اـِلَى عُنُقِهِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[sometimes] means (assumed tropical:)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His hand was withheld from expenditure."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A2-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gul~a","text_ar":"غُلَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yugal~u","text_ar":"يُغَلُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galalN","text_ar":"غَلَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", said of a man, (S,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, thirsty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemently thirsty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affected with burning of thirst,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"little"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"much;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA;) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with burning of the inside,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from thirst,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from anger and vexation."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.) ―         -b2-  And"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~a","text_ar":"غَلَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"said of a camel, (S, O, K,) originally"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galila","text_ar":"غَلِلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (MF, TA,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yagal~N","text_ar":"يَغَلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Agtl~","text_ar":"اغتلّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"also;"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, thirsty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"vehemently thirsty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"affected with burning of the inside:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he did not fully satisfy his thirst;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S and O in explanation of the former, and TA in explanation of both;) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~ato","text_ar":"غَلَّتْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is said of camels in like manner, agreeably with this last explanation: (K:) and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Aigotal~ato","text_ar":"اِغْتَلَّتْ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also said of sheep or goats, (K, TA,) signifying"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"they thirsted."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)       -A3-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~a Sadoruhu","text_ar":"غَلَّ صَدْرُهُ"},{"kind":"text","text":", aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yagil~N","text_ar":"يَغِلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O, K, TA, [in the CK, erroneously,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yagal~u","text_ar":"يَغَلُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":",]) with kesr, (S, O,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gil~N","text_ar":"غِلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", with kesr, (O,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"His bosom was,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"became, affected with rancour, malevolence, malice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spite:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, K:) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"with dishonesty,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"insincerity."},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O.) [See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gil~N","text_ar":"غِلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", below.] It is said in a trad.,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"valaAvN laA yagil~u Ealayohin~a qalobu Almuw^omini","text_ar":"ثَلَاثٌ لَا يَغِلُّ عَلَيْهِنَّ قَلْبُ المُوْمِنِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e. [There are"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"three"},{"kind":"text","text":"habits, ("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xiSaAl","text_ar":"خِصَال"},{"kind":"text","text":"being understood, these, as is said in the O, being “ the acting sincerely towards God, ” and “ giving honest counsel to those in command, ” and “ keeping to the community ” of the Muslims,)]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"while conforming to which the heart of the believer will not be invaded by rancour, malevolence, malice,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spite,"},{"kind":"text","text":"causing it to swerve from that which is right; (S, * O;) a saying of the Prophet; thus related by some: accord. to others, ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yugil~u","text_ar":"يُغِلُّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) with damm to the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Y","text_ar":"ى"},{"kind":"text","text":", (O,) which is from the meaning expl. in the next sentence here following. (S, * O.)       -A4-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~a","text_ar":"غَلَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, O, Msb, K,) aor."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yagul~u","text_ar":"يَغُلُّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, O,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guluwlN","text_ar":"غُلُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (S, Mgh, O, Msb, K,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He acted unfaithfully;"},{"kind":"text","text":"as also ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Agl~","text_ar":"اغلّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":": (S, O, Msb, K:) or thus the latter, (S, Mgh, O, Msb, K,) accord. to ISk (S, Msb) and A'Obeyd, (S,) in a general sense; (Mgh, Msb;) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he became unfaithful:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA:) but the former verb is used only in relation to spoil, or booty; (S, Mgh, O, * Msb, K;) you say,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~a mina Almagonami","text_ar":"غَلَّ مِنَ المَغْنَمِ"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"xaAna","text_ar":"خَانَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He acted unfaithfully in taking from the spoil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"booty"},{"kind":"text","text":"]; (S, O;) or meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he acted unfaithfully in relation to the spoil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"booty:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~a","text_ar":"غَلَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAth, Mgh, TA,) aor. as above, (Mgh,) inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guluwlN","text_ar":"غُلُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (IAth, TA,) or"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~N","text_ar":"غَلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", (Mgh, [thus in my copy, accord. to which it is trans., as will be shown by what follows,]) signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he stole;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"was unfaithful in respect of a thing privily;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and such conduct is termed"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"guluwlN","text_ar":"غُلُولٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"because, in the case thereof, the hands, or arms, have the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gul~","text_ar":"غُلّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"[q. v.] put upon them: (IAth, TA:) or it signifies also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took"},{"kind":"text","text":"a thing"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"and hid"},{"kind":"text","text":"it"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"amid his goods;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and it occurs in a trad. as meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he took"},{"kind":"text","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"$amolap","text_ar":"شَمْلَة"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"privily."},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh.) It is said in the Kur [iii. 155],"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wamaA kaAna linabiY~K A^ano yagul~a","text_ar":"وَمَا كَانَ لِنَبِىٍّ اَنْ يَغُلَّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^ano","text_ar":"اَنْ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"yugal~a","text_ar":"يُغَلَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":", accord. to different readers; the former meaning ["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"And it is not attributable to a prophet"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that he would act unfaithfully;"},{"kind":"text","text":"and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"An yugal~a","text_ar":"ان يُغَلَّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"meaning, [agreeably with an explanation of"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agal~a","text_ar":"اَغَلَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"fulaAnFA","text_ar":"فُلَانًا"},{"kind":"text","text":"in the K,]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that unfaithful conduct should be imputed to him;"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that there should be taken from his"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"share of the"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"spoil,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"booty;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, TA;) [or this may mean,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that he should be found to be acting unfaithfully;"},{"kind":"text","text":"for, accord. to the TA,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Agl~ Alr~ajula","text_ar":"اغلّ الرَّجُلَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"means"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"wajadahu gaAl~FA","text_ar":"وَجَدَهُ غَالًّا"},{"kind":"text","text":";] but IB says that a pass. aor. is seldom found in the language of the Arabs in a phrase of this kind. (TA.) And it is said in a trad."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"walaA A_isolaAla","text_ar":"وَلَا اـِسْلَالَ"},{"kind":"text","text":"↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"laA A_igolaAla","text_ar":"لَا اـِغْلَالَ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"There shall be no acting unfaithfully nor stealing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"there shall be no act of bribery"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"nor stealing"},{"kind":"text","text":"]: (S, O:) or, as some say,"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"there shall be no aiding"},{"kind":"text","text":"another"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"to act unfaithfully"},{"kind":"text","text":"[&c.]. (TA.)       -A5-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galalotu liln~aAqapi","text_ar":"غَلَلْتُ لِلنَّاقَةِ"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"I fed the she-camel with"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galiyl","text_ar":"غَلِيل"},{"kind":"text","text":"i. e."},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"date-stones mixed with"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the species of trefoil called"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qit~","text_ar":"قِتّ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (S, * O, TA.)       -A6-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~a AlA_ihaAba","text_ar":"غَلَّ الاـِهَابَ"},{"kind":"text","text":": see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"A^agal~a fiY AlA_ihaAbi","text_ar":"اَغَلَّ فِى الاـِهَابِ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A7-"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~a","text_ar":"غَلَّ"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"EalaY Al$~aYo'i","text_ar":"عَلَى الشَّىْءِ"},{"kind":"text","text":", inf. n."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~N","text_ar":"غَلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":"; and ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Agl~","text_ar":"اغلّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":";"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"He was silent at the thing:"},{"kind":"text","text":"and also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"he was intent upon the thing."},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA.)"}],"source_refs":["S","K","TA","O","TK","MF","Mgh","Msb","IAth"]},{"entry_id":"n32168","headword_ar":"غَلَّةٌ","root":"gl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Proceeds, revenue,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"income,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, K, TA, [in the CK,"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~axalapu","text_ar":"الدَّخَلَةُ"},{"kind":"text","text":"is put for"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Ald~axolu","text_ar":"الدَّخْلُ"},{"kind":"text","text":",])"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"of any kind,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb,)"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"accruing from the produce,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"yield, of land,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, K, TA,) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the rent thereof,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb, TA,) [in which sense ↓"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"magal~N","text_ar":"مَغَلٌّ","orth_type":"arrow"},{"kind":"text","text":"is also used, as a subst., pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"mugal~aAtN","text_ar":"مُغَلَّاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":",] or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from seed-produce,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from fruits,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from milk,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from hire,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the increase of cattle,"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the rent of a house,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"from the hire of a slave,"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, K, TA,) and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(Mgh, Msb;) [generally meaning"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"corn,"},{"kind":"text","text":"or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"grain;"},{"kind":"text","text":"i.e.]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"wheat"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"barley"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"rice"},{"kind":"text","text":"and"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the like;"},{"kind":"text","text":"(KL;) the"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~ap","text_ar":"غَلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"of the slave is the"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"payment imposed by the master, and made to him:"},{"kind":"text","text":"(TA voce"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"DariybapN","text_ar":"ضَرِيبَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":":) pl."},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~aAtN","text_ar":"غَلَّاتٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":"(S, O, Msb, TA) and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gilaAlN","text_ar":"غِلَالٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":". (Msb, TA.) ―         -b2-  Also"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"Dirhems"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieces of money"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that are clipped"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"muqaT~aEap","text_ar":"مُقَطَّعَة"},{"kind":"text","text":"),"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"in a single piece thereof"},{"kind":"text","text":"["},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"the quantity clipped being"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"qiyraAT","text_ar":"قِيرَاط"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"or a"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"Tas~uwj","text_ar":"طَسُّوج"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"or a grain;"},{"kind":"text","text":"of which it is said in the “ Eedáh, ” that one's lending"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gal~ap","text_ar":"غَلَّة"},{"kind":"text","text":"in order to have such as are free from defect returned to him is disapproved: (Mgh:) or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"dirhems"},{"kind":"text","text":"[or"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"pieces of money"},{"kind":"text","text":"]"},{"kind":"italic_en","text":"that are rejected by the treasury of the state, but taken by the merchants."},{"kind":"text","text":"(KT. [Freytag has given this latter explanation, but has erroneously assigned it to"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gul~apN","text_ar":"غُلَّةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".])"}],"source_refs":["Mgh","Msb","K","TA","S","O"]},{"entry_id":"n32169","headword_ar":"غُلَّةٌ","root":"gl","body":[{"kind":"italic_en","text":"A thing in which one hides himself."},{"kind":"text","text":"(IAar, TA.) ―         -b2-  See also"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gilaAlapN","text_ar":"غِلَالَةٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":", in two places: ―         -b3-  and"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"galalN","text_ar":"غَلَلٌ"},{"kind":"text","text":".       -A2-  And see"},{"kind":"arabic","text_bw":"gul~N","text_ar":"غُلٌّ"},{"kind":"text","text":", last sentence."}],"source_refs":[]}]},"classical_definitions":null}